item.description:
Dear Members:
We have rescheduled to trip to the MFA to explore the Egyptian collection to Wednesday, February 4. Please join us. The museum entrance is free that night.

In a follow up to lecture on the Transforming Power of Myth in Ancient Egypt (January 21, 2009), we will visit the Egyptian Exhibit in the Museum of Fine Arts

• We will meet at the Fenway Entrance of the MFA
• Reservations online required
• Session I, held on January 21st, is recommended but not required

Tour Fee: $5

This will be a very exciting and exceptional lecture/tour.

Join us
